  <h2 class="main-title-100 my-8">Become a Booksie</h2>

    <span class="icon-violet-300 text-center text-3xl block" data-read-more-target="arrowDown" data-action="click->read-more#openForm"><i class="fa-solid fa-angles-down"></i></span>

